@startuml Order_Lifecycle
title Order Lifecycle Flow

actor "Customer" as Customer
actor "Merchant" as Merchant
participant "Merchant Dashboard\n(Next.js)" as MUI
participant "Customer Storefront\n(Next.js)" as CUI
participant "Order Service\n(Spring Boot)" as OS
participant "PostgreSQL DB" as DB
participant "Notification Service" as Notify

== Order Created (from Checkout) ==

note over OS, DB
  Order created during checkout with status PENDING.
  Paymob/Wallet orders move to CONFIRMED immediately.
  COD orders remain PENDING until merchant confirms.
end note

OS -> Notify : Notify Merchant\n"New order received #{orderId}"
OS -> Notify : Notify Customer\n"Order placed successfully #{orderId}"

== Merchant Reviews Order ==

Merchant -> MUI : Open Orders panel
MUI -> OS : GET /orders/store/{storeId}\n+ Bearer Token
OS -> DB : Query orders for this store
DB --> OS : Return orders list
OS --> MUI : Orders list
MUI --> Merchant : Display orders

Merchant -> MUI : Open order #{orderId}
MUI -> OS : GET /orders/{orderId}
OS -> DB : Query full order details\n{items, customer, address,\npayment method, total, tracking}
DB --> OS : Return order details
OS --> MUI : Full order details
MUI --> Merchant : Show order details page

== Merchant Confirms Order ==

Merchant -> MUI : Click "Confirm Order"
MUI -> OS : PUT /orders/{orderId}/status\n{status: CONFIRMED}
OS -> DB : Update order {status: CONFIRMED}
OS -> Notify : Notify Customer\n"Your order has been confirmed"
OS --> MUI : 200 OK
MUI --> Merchant : Order marked as CONFIRMED ✅

== Merchant Ships Order ==

Merchant -> MUI : Click "Mark as Shipped"\n+ enter tracking details
MUI -> OS : PUT /orders/{orderId}/status\n{status: SHIPPED,\n trackingNumber, shippingCarrier}
OS -> DB : Update order\n{status: SHIPPED,\n trackingNumber, shippingCarrier}
OS -> Notify : Notify Customer\n"Your order has been shipped"
OS --> MUI : 200 OK
MUI --> Merchant : Order marked as SHIPPED 🚚

== Customer Tracks Order ==

Customer -> CUI : Open "My Orders"
CUI -> OS : GET /orders/me + Bearer Token
OS -> DB : Query customer orders
DB --> OS : Return orders with tracking info
OS --> CUI : Orders list including tracking details
CUI --> Customer : Show orders with current status\n& tracking number

== Merchant Marks as Delivered ==

Merchant -> MUI : Click "Mark as Delivered"
MUI -> OS : PUT /orders/{orderId}/status\n{status: DELIVERED}
OS -> DB : Update order {status: DELIVERED}
OS -> Notify : Notify Customer\n"Your order has been delivered! 🎉"
OS -> Notify : Notify Merchant\n"Order #{orderId} marked as delivered"
OS --> MUI : 200 OK
MUI --> Merchant : Order marked as DELIVERED ✅

== COD Payment Confirmation (COD only) ==

note over Merchant, OS
  Merchant collects cash on delivery,
  then confirms payment received.
end note

Merchant -> MUI : Click "Confirm Payment Received"
MUI -> OS : POST /payments/{paymentId}/confirm
OS -> DB : Update payment status
OS -> Notify : Notify Customer\n"COD payment confirmed"
OS --> MUI : 200 OK
MUI --> Merchant : Payment marked as collected 💰

@enduml
